You are not getting the textview references correctly. Even if you passed them correctly from the Activity, it is not correct to change views from a Service. Activities have a different lifecycle than a Service, and trying to reference a textview which does not exist will surely result in a crash.

```
else {
    builder.setSmallIcon(R.drawable.ic_launcher_background);
    builder.setContentTitle(&quot;EÄim&quot;);
    builder.setContentText(&quot;X : &quot; + event.values[0] + &quot; Y : &quot; + event.values[1] + &quot; Z : &quot; + event.values[2]);
    //...
